These may be difficult to control in desktop as it requires holding the controller which could potentially make it difficult to see where one is going.
===Fast travel===
[[File:Sketchu Spring FastTravel.webp|thumb|a fast travel point in Mushroom Rocks|195x195px]]Fast travel points can be found across the world, when interacted with, it'll unlock a diamond behind spawn on the air balloon. Unlocking a fast travel point unlocks it for all users in the instance. They are visible from the distance due to being rendered over the sandstorm. Fast travel points are not persistent and will have to be unlocked again once entering a new instance.